All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AbstractBaseObject
The AbstractBaseObject is an abstract class providing a base structure for objects with a unique identifier (id) and a name.
BootService
The BootstrapService interface defines the contract for services that require initialization parameters during bootstrap.
BootServiceImpl
Implementation of the BootService interface for initializing service parameters.
CalculationResultMemoryService
This interface defines the contract for a service responsible for handling memory operations related to calculation results.
CalculationResultMemoryServiceImpl
This service class implements the CalculationResultMemoryService interface to handle the memory operations related to calculation results.
CalculationService
An interface representing a service for performing calculations.
CalculationServiceImpl
A service implementation for performing calculations based on model run configuration data.
CellProcessingService
Defines a service for calculating time series data for a cell's properties over a sequence of timesteps in a simulation.
CellProcessingServiceImpl
Service implementation for cell calculations.
CellTimestep
Represents a timestep in the simulation for a specific cell.
DischargeDataMemoryService
An interface representing a service for saving discharge data in memory.
DischargeDataMemoryServiceImpl
An implementation of the DischargeDataMemoryService interface that saves discharge data in memory.
ErosionLogic
The ErosionLogic interface defines a method for calculating the sediment transport coefficient based on specified erosion-related parameters.
ErosionLogicImpl
The ErosionLogicImpl class is an implementation of the ErosionLogic interface, providing a method to calculate the sediment transport coefficient based on specified parameters.
FirstOrderDifferentialEquationsService
Defines a service for providing first-order ordinary differential equations (ODEs) for a Pandora simulation.
FirstOrderDifferentialEquationsServiceImpl
Implementation of the FirstOrderDifferentialEquationsService interface that provides the first-order ordinary differential equations (ODEs) for a Pandora simulation.
FixCellDataMemoryService
An interface representing a service for handling FixCellData in memory.
FixCellDataMemoryServiceImpl
Service implementation for managing fixed cell data in memory.
ModelRunConfigurationMemoryService
An interface representing a service for managing model run configurations in memory.
ModelRunConfigurationMemoryServiceImpl
A service implementation for managing model run configurations in memory.
PandoraDifferentialEquations
A class representing a set of first-order ordinary differential equations (ODEs) for simulating chemical processes with PANDORA.
PandoraIntegratorService
Defines a service for performing numerical integration of Pandora simulations.
PandoraIntegratorServiceImpl
Implementation of the PandoraIntegratorService interface.
PandoraTimestep
The PandoraTimestep class represents a specific time step in the Pandora model, characterized by initial values, start and end times, dimensionality, discharge, volume, terrestrial and upstream sources, and other properties.
ReactionCalculationService
An interface representing a service for calculating reactions based on an array of values.
ReactionCalculationServiceImpl
A service implementation for calculating reactions.
ShearStressLogic
The ShearStressLogic interface defines methods for calculating shear stress, critical shear stress for sediment transport, and the Shields parameter based on specified parameters.
ShearStressLogicImpl
The ShearStressLogicImpl class is an implementation of the ShearStressLogic interface, providing methods to calculate shear stress, critical shear stress for sediment transport, and the Shields parameter based on specified parameters.
SpecieConfigurationMemoryService
The SpecieConfigurationMemoryService interface provides methods for storage operations on specie configurations.
SpecieConfigurationMemoryServiceImpl
A service implementation for managing specie configurations in memory.
TemporalCellDataMemoryService
A service interface for saving and retrieving temporal cell data from memory.
TemporalCellDataMemoryServiceImpl<T extends com.pandora.calculation.repositories.TemporalCellDataRepository>
An abstract implementation of TemporalCellDataMemoryService that delegates data storage and retrieval operations to a provided TemporalCellDataRepository.
TerrestrialInputDataMemoryService
This interface defines the contract for a service responsible for managing terrestrial input data in memory.
TerrestrialInputDataMemoryServiceImpl
Service implementation for managing terrestrial input data in memory.
TransportCalculationService
Defines a service for calculating transport phenomena in a chemical simulation.
TransportCalculationServiceImpl
Implementation of the TransportCalculationService interface that calculates the transport of chemical species within a simulation.
UpstreamInputCalculationService
Interface for calculating upstream inputs.
UpstreamInputCalculationServiceImpl
Service implementation for calculating upstream inputs.
VolumeDataMemoryService
An interface representing a service for saving volume data in memory.
VolumeDataMemoryServiceImpl
An implementation of the VolumeDataMemoryService interface that saves volume data in memory.
